nnoremap <f1> :BufExplorer<cr>
nnoremap <f2> :NERDTreeToggle<cr>
nnoremap <leader>ev <C-w><C-v><C-l>:e $MYVIMRC<cr>
nnoremap <leader>g :Gbrowse<CR>
"key mapping for window resizing
nnoremap <S-Up> <C-W>+
nnoremap <S-Down> <C-W>-
nnoremap <S-Left> <C-w><
nnoremap <S-Right> <C-w>>
